text: Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs, also known as Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs: The Series, is an American-Canadian animated television series developed by Mark Evestaff and Alex Galatis for Cartoon Network in the United States and YTV in Canada. ==References== Category:2010s American animated television series Category:2017 American television series debuts Category:2018 American television series endings Category:2017 Canadian television series debuts Category:2018 Canadian television series endings Category:English-language television programs
